{"tid":1986150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"只要有人講 我就會再同手足一齊出黎","createTime":"2020-04-23T15:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T17:26:31.000Z","uid":140620,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"645f563ea87528b7b87babbcb9627beb85e5f09b","tid":1986150,"uid":140620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"抗疫咗好耐，武漢肺炎未必真係退咗，但打倒極權嘅心不可失。我係一個因為&ldquo;抗疫&rdquo;而退咗落黎嘅人，一直等待手足嘅號召而再次一齊走上街頭。本身一直諗住等武漢肺炎冇咁嚴重先再出去，但今日見到哩條片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2864078490357684&amp;id=345110412254517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2864078490357684%26id%3D345110412254517&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=71c2d1bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2864078490357684&amp;id=345110412254517</a><br />\n法國嘅疫情比香港嚴重，但人民為人民發聲嘅事實都係冇變。自從一個月確診數目爆升，人人留係屋企開始我已經係屋企操體能，只想講一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足，我準備好返黎，就等你一句</span><br />\n我知道好多人都等緊，但我哋等緊嘅同時，每日都有手足被捕被殺，我哋唔等得。只要有人講一聲，就算重光又好六四又好，六一二又好，圍狗屋，我都準備好。而家我想問你哋一句，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你準備好未？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"072a16cace282acd48e39e449bda66a9d47bdde7","tid":1986150,"uid":140620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"我可能打得悶，但希望各位可以睇一睇，俾個答覆我"},{"pid":"0659e81b9a557c0ac849a6bdca98e0c8f990f992","tid":1986150,"uid":140620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:49:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e15f4ea0873243d66d84c89f9583830c36f6f25","tid":1986150,"uid":140620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:49:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1968ef96d17a301e602bf1a8e2ea6b315354890b","tid":1986150,"uid":140620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6002862ad3bcad95814732b5740267d9149aff9","tid":1986150,"uid":140620,"like":0